      <title>特朗普审判外自焚男子因伤重死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-19/police-to-review-security-outside-courthouse-hosting-trump-s-trial-after-man-sets-himself-on-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——警方称，一名男子在前总统唐纳德·特朗普受审的法院外浇上助燃剂并自焚，现已死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-19/police-to-review-security-outside-courthouse-hosting-trump-s-trial-after-man-sets-himself-on-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在纽约市特朗普审判外自焚的男子已经死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/man-who-self-immolated-outside-nyc-trump-trial-in-critical-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美联社援引警方消息称，一名佛罗里达州男子在曼哈顿市中心法院大楼外自焚，唐纳德·特朗普的刑事审判正在进行中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/man-who-self-immolated-outside-nyc-trump-trial-in-critical-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:11:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乍得要求美国停止战略陆军基地的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/chad-asks-us-troops-to-cease-operations-at-strategic-army-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍得呼吁美国从中非国家的一个军事基地撤军，该基地是西方为数不多的打击该地区激烈圣战叛乱的前哨基地之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/chad-asks-us-troops-to-cease-operations-at-strategic-army-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
